[b][span style='color: #E80000;']IMPORTANT 1!![/span][/b] --&gt; Next to this container, you will have to install a PostgreSQL container from the APPS, any version 11 or 12 will do.
User:
DB name: dsmrreader
DB user: dsmrreader
DB password: dsmrreader
