DATALOGGER INPUT METHOD=serial[br]
DATALOGGER_SERIAL_PORT=/dev/ttyUSB0[br]
DATALOGGER_SERIAL_BAUDRATE=115200[br]
[br]
[span style='color: #E80000;']and set your device to the right USB path[/span]
&lt;/br&gt;
